;ATOMS WITH ZERO OCCUPANCY:
--------------------------
90 ATOMS WERE NOT SUFFICIENTLY ORDERED IN THE CRYSTAL TO 
CONTRIBUTE SIGNIFICANTLY TO THE FOURIER MAP.  THESE ATOMS 
WERE SET TO ZERO OCCUPANCY AND HAD THEIR B-EQ'S AND ANISOU 
EIGENVALUES SET TO ZERO. 

