NON-CRYSTALLOGRAPHIC SYMMETRY
THE TRANSFORMATIONS PRESENTED ON THE MTRIX RECORDS BELOW
DESCRIBE NON-CRYSTALLOGRAPHIC RELATIONSHIPS AMONG ATOMS
IN THIS ENTRY.  APPLYING THE APPROPRIATE MTRIX
TRANSFORMATION TO THE RESIDUES LISTED FIRST WILL YIELD
